<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="for-so-long">for (so) long</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>长久地；长时间地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Danny has worked hard for long to realize his dream.
为实现梦想，丹尼一直在努力工作。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sorry I haven't written for so long.
真抱歉，我好长时间没给你写信了。</p><footer>译林② – 2</footer></div></div>